sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as "Tez Client API"
    participant RM as "YARN Resource Manager"
    participant NM as "YARN Node Manager"
    participant AM as "Tez ApplicationMaster"
    participant Containers as "Task Containers"

    Client->>RM: 1. Request Application Submission
    RM-->>Client: 2. Return Application ID & Resource Limits
    Client->>RM: 3. Submit Application (specifies AM settings & jars)
    RM->>NM: 4. Launch Tez AM Container
    NM->>AM: 5. Start Tez AM JVM
    AM->>RM: 6. Register AM (starts heartbeat & query status)
    AM->>RM: 7. Request allocations for Vertex Tasks
    RM->>AM: 8. Allocate Container resources
    AM->>NM: 9. Launch Task Containers
    NM->>Containers: 10. Run Task JVMs
    Containers-->>AM: 11. Report Status/Progress (Heartbeats)
    AM->>RM: 12. Unregister AM when DAG completes
